{"tid":277247,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"【Uber筆戰】創科局狠批：Uber知法犯法、不負責任","createTime":"2017-06-09T12:24:06.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-09T17:30:16.000Z","uid":17738,"like":0,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"6f13a71bfa5d09980ed2fc8d25f63fe51c997cc4","tid":277247,"uid":17738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T12:24:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/e-paper/20170609/large/1497009755_9572.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170609%2Flarge%2F1497009755_9572.jpg&h=994a0ac4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/e-paper/20170609/large/1497010029_0f4f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170609%2Flarge%2F1497010029_0f4f.jpg&h=666e114f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n創新及科技局局長楊偉雄，近日就Uber合法性問題，向公共政策顧問李兆富下筆戰戰書。正當李兆富已再發文反擊楊偉雄討論失焦時，創新及科技局局於Facebook發帖，狠批Uber知法犯法！全文如下：<br />\n<br />\n「Uber用大數據技術提供了兩項所謂創新共享經濟服務業務：Uber電召車和UberEATS。Uber電召車被裁定違法，但UberEATS卻合法。可見Uber是完全有選擇採取合法或違法方式推動共享經濟。<br />\n<br />\nUber知法犯法，不但沒有自我檢討，更令非其僱員的電召司機繼續違法取酬載客而被捕。這是以創新共享經濟為藉口，為自身商業利益而不負責任的做法！<br />\n<br />\nUber常說很多地方都容許其經營。它為何就不提一下南韓、泰國、荷蘭、德國、法國和西班牙等國家，都已裁定Uber電召車為違法商業模式或提出檢控呢！」<br />\n<br />\n然而，李兆富重申的兩條問題，即政府究竟有何具體指標，去判斷何謂「大多數人意見」；以及政府可有計劃在可見將來就「不合時宜的法例」進行公眾諮詢及公開討論，當局均未有回應。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56807291&amp;category_guid=7015342&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170609\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56807291%26category_guid%3D7015342%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170609&d=lcEK0%2F7e%2FofNWhS4pCQShf6YfqAiA4jm3R2Vm1010vU%3D&h=037ca4e8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56807291%26category_guid%3D7015342%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170609&h=3aaedf6c\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56807291&amp;category_guid=7015342&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170609</a>"},{"pid":"f8d5f0b2a043fe0d78b86a1e64d613cc6d72e0ec","tid":277247,"uid":8000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T13:01:32.000Z","msg":"笑死"},{"pid":"de4127d2d8c3ef5d52b5f98aa2f0126ec7337247","tid":277247,"uid":73092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T13:18:40.000Z","msg":"有邊個見過Steve Jobs？未呀？我見過！我真係見過！"},{"pid":"189711491cf8406c70a3c450f1c5005648252435","tid":277247,"uid":76591,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T13:23:05.000Z","msg":"請問係邊個將uber引入香港架？<br />\n同HKTV單嘢一撚樣，批咗幅地畀wiki然後唔發牌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"41869112f1e412863c95fffd2b5d1c571d6eed65","tid":277247,"uid":119996,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T14:51:27.000Z","msg":"官字十個口啦"},{"pid":"60c8fa10f4d8c1043cd9ff93b93f6922ae4d55d2","tid":277247,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T17:30:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有邊個見過Steve Jobs？未呀？我見過！我真係見過！</blockquote><br />\n楊乜乜=死台狗"}]}